generates C4172:  \n  \n```  \n// C4172.cpp  \n// compile with: /W1 /LD  \nfloat f = 10;  \n  \nconst double& bar() {  \n// try the following line instead  \n// const float& bar() {  \n   return f;   // C4172  \n}  \n```"}